{"tid":1031683,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"（世界盡頭）朝聖之旅找伴","createTime":"2019-02-21T21:39:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-23T15:52:21.000Z","uid":198715,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"44b38cb581cfe4d39085d7b956f4570c51e2d5f0","tid":1031683,"uid":198715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T21:39:25.000Z","msg":"睇完wifi巴嘅post，決定咗人生點都要行一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n暫時預定係行法國之路 預計30-40日內行完<br />\nBudget 20k 我諗應該夠應付成個行程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇巴打想一齊行，旅途中做個伴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n始終一個人去安全問題都想搵個伴安心一齊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n暫定係5月中至6中依段時間，如果夾到<br />\n時間可以就翻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果唔係，睇怕我要開始人生第一個毒遊了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dfc13bc0b07387a75c20eec66c8aa024da156fe","tid":1031683,"uid":34634,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T01:36:57.000Z","msg":"小弟應該今年8,9月先去，打算獨行<br />\n<br />\n加油！"},{"pid":"6f3864d865f2ce49d6ce5c1bbb252c1aa6c19173","tid":1031683,"uid":198715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6dfc13bc0b07387a75c20eec66c8aa024da156fe","tid":1031683,"uid":34634,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T01:36:57.000Z","msg":"小弟應該今年8,9月先去，打算獨行<br />\n<br />\n加油！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T06:31:02.000Z","msg":"巴打加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望大家都有個一生難忘嘅回憶"},{"pid":"750b778516a2648cff309c8da2ddbbb8b62dd47d","tid":1031683,"uid":42338,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T06:50:42.000Z","msg":"過來人表示獨行會舒服啲<br />\n唔使就人哋步速<br />\n路上都會自然識到旅伴<br />\n<br />\n有問題上連登問都有好多巴絲行過會答你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><b